**0.25%\n|4,080\n**0.25%\n|\n[\nXAUEGP\nGold 18 Karat] |3,480\n**0.24%\n|3,497.25\n**0.25%\n|\n[\nXAUEGP\nGold 14 Karat] |2,706.75\n\nTitle: Gold Price Today in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP), Egypt Gold Rate\nAuthor: www.moneycurrencyconverter.com\nPublished Date: 2025-05-15T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://www.moneycurrencyconverter.com/gold-prices-today-in-egypt.html\nText: Gold Price Today in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP), Egypt Gold Rate\n\n# Current Gold Price Today in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP)\n\n1 Gold Ounce = 249,961.54 EGP 1 Gram Gold = 8,036.45 Egyptian Pound\n\nGold price in Egypt is calculated both per ounce, gram, kilogram and tola and for the most common karats. The following table displays current gold rates in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP) for troy ounce, kilogram, tael, tola, pennyweight, grain and gram of different karats. Troy ounce is a traditional unit of gold weight. Gold prices per troy ounce are converted from USD to Egyptian Pound according to the latest exchange rates where 1 USD = 47.49 Egyptian Pound .\n\n## Price of Gold in Egyptian Pound\n\n| Gold Unit | Gold Price (EGP) |\n| --- | --- |\n| 1 Gram Gold | 8,036.45 EGP |\n| 1 Troy Ounce Gold | 249,961.54 EGP |\n| 1 Kilogram Gold | 8,036,450.11 EGP |\n| 1 Tael Gold | 300,796.22 EGP |\n| 1 Tola Gold | 93,735.58 EGP |\n| 1 Pennyweight Gold | 12,498.08 EGP |\n| 1 Grain Gold | 520.75 EGP |\n\nThe most commonly u\n\nTitle: Gold price in Egypt rises again, 24 Carat at ₤5,354 (₹9,744) per gram on September 1, 2025\nAuthor: TOI World Desk  / TIMESOFINDIA.COM /  Updated: Sep 01, 2025, 10:59 IST\nPublished Date: 2025-09-01T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gold-price-in-egypt-rises-again-24-carat-at-5354-9253-per-gram-on-september-1-2025/articleshow/123626298.cms\nText: Gold price in Egypt rises again, 24 Carat at ₤5,354 (₹9,744) per gram on September 1, 2025 | World News - The Times of India\n\nEdition\n\nIN\n\n- [US] \n- [IN] \n\nEnglish\n\n- [ગુજરાતી] \n- [తెలుగు] \n- [മലയാളം] \n- [বাংলা] \n- [தமிழ்] \n- [ಕನ್ನಡ] \n- [मराठी] \n- [हिन्दी] \n- [English] \n\n[Weather] \n\nSign In\n\n- Gold price in Egypt rises again, 24 Carat at ₤5,354 (₹9,744) per gram on September 1, 2025\n- [Middle East News] \n- [World News] \n- [News] \n\nTrending\n\n[Minnesota church shooting] \n\n[Trump Health] \n\n[Texas I-20 crash] \n\n[Rudy Giuliani] \n\n# Gold price in Egypt rises again, 24 Carat at ₤5,354 (₹9,744) per gram on September 1, 2025\n\nShare\n\nAA\n\n+Text Size\n\n- Large\n- Medium\n- Small\n\nGold prices in Egypt climbed on September 1, 2025, with 24-carat gold reaching ₤5,354 (₹9,744) and 21-carat at ₤4,685 (₹8,526) per gram. The rise follows global gold hitting a four-m\n\nTitle: Gold price in Egypt on 31-01-2026\nAuthor: gold-price-daily.com\nPublished Date: 2026-01-30T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://en.gold-price-daily.com/gold-eg/2026-01-31/\nText: Gold price in Egypt on 31-01-2026\n\nLast updated 5 minutes\n\n# Gold price on 31-01-2026 in Egypt in EGP\n\nOn this page, gold prices in Egypt are displayed in the EGP currency, as gold prices in Egypt are updated and monitored every 15 minutes, and thus you can follow the price of a gram of gold in Egypt periodically and continuously.\n\n### Gold prices in Egypt at closing on 31-01-2026\n\n| Unit | Price in EGP | Price in USD |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| 1 kg (24 karat) | 7378205.56 | 157356.40 |\n| Ounce (24 karat) | 229487.79 | 4894.33 |\n| 1 gm (24 karat) | 7378.37 | 157.36 |\n| 1 gm (23 karat) | 7070.79 | 150.80 |\n| 1 gm (22 karat) | 6763.20 | 144.24 |\n| 1 gm (21 karat) | 6456.08 | 137.69 |\n| 1 gm (18 karat) | 5533.78 | 118.02 |\n\nOn this page, we have displayed the price of gold on 31-01-2026 in Egypt in all types of internationally recognized karats, in addition to the price of a kilo of gold in Egypt and the price of an ounce of gold in Egypt in the EGP currency, where you can view the prices directly, which helps you in analysis and decision-making in a better way.\n\n\n\nTitl