{"type":"message","id":"0fa3faf0","parentId":"b03391c4","timestamp":"2026-02-28T14:07:53.482Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call-8bcbcc4d-6f4e-4923-99e4-39309f2c08fa","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: Gold Price in Egypt Today – Live 24K, 22K, 21K Rates in EGP\nAuthor: \nPublished Date: 2025-03-04T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://goldpriceme.com/gold-price-in-egypt/\nText: Gold Price in Egypt Today – Live 24K, 22K, 21K Rates in EGP\n[\n![Gold Price in KSA, Bahrain, Dubai, Oman, Kuwait, Egypt] ] \n# Gold Price in Egypt\nLast Update:\nLoading…\n###\n24 Karat/ Gram\nEGP 6,199.32\n###\n22 Karat/ Gram\nEGP 5,690.89\n###\n18 Karat/ Gram\nEGP 4,649.24\n*Live from Cairo &amp; Alexandria | Daily Updates for Egyptians, Expats &amp; GCC Investors*\n \n# Gold Price in Egypt\nGold Rate in Egypt today per gram are approximately:\n* 24K Gold: EGP 6,199.32\n* 22K Gold: EGP 5,690.89 \n* 21K Gold: EGP 5,424.28\n* 18K Gold: EGP 4,649.24\n## Gold Price in Egypt Per Gram &amp; Tola\n|Gold Purity|Per Gram|Per Tola|\n|24K Gold|EGP 6,199.32|EGP 72,323.60|\n|22K Gold|EGP 5,690.89 |EGP 66,392.98|\n|21K Gold|EGP 5,424.28|EGP 63247.1048|\n|18K Gold|EGP 4,649.24|EGP 54,242.45|\n|14K Gold|EGP 3,626.45|EGP 42,308.89|\n|10K Gold|EGP 2,584.72 |EGP 30,158.36|\n![Egypt Flag] \n##\nEgypt Major Cities Gold Rates Today (1 gram)\nEGP per gram | Updated\n|City|18K|22K|24K|\nSource: Egypt Gold Association | 0% VAT on Gold\n## 1 Tola Gold Price in Egypt\n|Per Tola|Today Gold Price|\n|24K Gold 1 Tola|EGP 72,\n\nTitle: Egypt Gold Price Live - 24-hour (gold prices in Egyptian pounds EGP)\nURL: https://www.livepriceofgold.com/egypt-gold-price.html\nText: Egypt Gold Price Live - 24-hour (gold prices in Egyptian pounds EGP)\n[\n![Live Price of Gold Logo]] \n![live] \n*\n![Live SPOT Gold] SPOT GOLD\n5185.97 $\n**0.01**% (0.75)\nHigh:**5198.92** | Low:**5172.16**\n*\n![Gold Price per Gram] PER GRAM\n166.7514 $\n**0.02**\nHigh:**167.17** | Low:**166.31**\n*\n![Gold Tola Price] PER TOLA\n1 944.956 $\n**0.28**\nHigh:**1949.81** | Low:**1939.78**\n*\nEURO/DOLLAR\n1.1807 $\n**0.04**%\nHigh:**1.1820** | Low:**1.1790**\n*\n![Spot Silver Price] SPOT SILVER\n89.803 $\n**1.76**% (1.58)\nHigh:**90.522** | Low:**88.050**\n* [Live Gold Price] \n* [Gold Calculator ] \n* [Silver Price] \n* [Silver Calculator ] \n* [live Exchange Rate] \n* [Egypt Gold Price] \n* [Silver Price] \n* [EGP live] \n* [Gram] \n* [Ounce] \n* [Tola] \n* [22-Karat] \n# Gold Price in Egypt Today\nLivePriceofGold.com provides the latest gold prices for Egypt. Market and Local Prices (informal, parallel) are updated in real-time. ([سعر الذهب] \n)\n![Egypt] \n## Gold Rate in Egypt live\nLivePriceofGold provides live rates for gold in Egypt, spanning a range of purities including 24K, 22K, 21K, 18K, and 14K.\n[**Live**] update:\n27 Febru\n\nTitle: Gold Price Today in Egypt - سعر الذهب اليوم في مصر\nURL: https://egypt.instantgoldprice.com/en/\nText: Gold Price Today in Egypt – تابع سعر الذهب اليوم في جمهورية مصر العربية بشكل مباشر بعملة جنيه مصري والدولار، لجميع أنواع العيارات، بالإضافة لمعلومات عن أسعار الصرف\n\nJoin the Gold Price channel in Egypt on Telegram\n\nJoin Channel\n\n# Gold Price Today in Egypt\n\nTrack real-time gold and silver prices in Egypt updated every 10 seconds. Prices are displayed in Egyptian Pound (EGP). Get the latest market data, price history, and currency exchange rates for informed investment decisions.\n\nLive Prices\n\nEgyptian Pound US Dollar\n\nEGP\n\nOunce\n\n244,730.58\n\n+0.00 +0.00% ➤\n\nEGP\n\nGram\n\n7,868.27\n\n+0.00 +0.00% ➤\n\nChange from yesterday\n\nIncrease\n\nDecrease\n\nMarket is closed — opens after: 00:00:00\n\nNote: Prices from the trading market may differ slightly in the local market.\n\n## Gold vs Silver Today in USD\n\n🥇 Gold\n\n5,103.70\n\n+0.00\n\n+0.00%➤\n\n🥈 Silver\n\n84.63\n\n+0.00\n\n+0.00%➤\n\n| Metal | Price per Ounce | Change Amount | Change Percentage |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n\n## Gold Prices by Carat Today in Egyptian Pound\n\n| Carat | Price per Gram | Price per Gram |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| [Gold 24k Carat] | 7,868.27 | 164.09 |\n| [Gold 22k Carat] | 7,212.58\n\nTitle: Gold Price Today in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP), Egypt Gold Rate\nAuthor: www.moneycurrencyconverter.com\nPublished Date: 2025-05-15T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://www.moneycurrencyconverter.com/gold-prices-today-in-egypt.html\nText: Gold Price Today in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP), Egypt Gold Rate\n[![Money Currency Converter, Foreign Exchange Rates, Live Exchange Table]] \n* [Currencies] \n* [World Currencies] \n* [Cross Rates] \n* [Foreign Currency Exchange Rates] \n* [![MoneyCurrencyConverter.com Money Currency Converter Facebook Page]] \n# Current Gold Price Today in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP)\n1. [Money Currency Converter] \n2. [World Gold Prices] \n3. Gold Prices in Egypt\n1 Gold Ounce = 249,961.54 EGP\n1 Gram Gold = 8,036.45 Egyptian Pound\nGold price in Egypt is calculated both per ounce, gram, kilogram and tola and for the most common karats. The following table displays current gold rates in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP) for troy ounce, kilogram, tael, tola, pennyweight, grain and gram of different karats. Troy ounce is a traditional unit of gold weight. Gold prices per troy ounce are converted from USD to Egyptian Pound according to the latest exchange rates where 1 USD = 47.49 Egyptian Pound .\n## Price of Gold in Egyptian \n\nTitle: Gold price today in Egypt\nURL: https://pricegold.net/eg-egypt/\nText: Gold price today in Egypt\n[![Gold price today] Gold priceToday] \n2:47:01 PMNY Time\nFriday, January 30, 2026\nEnglish\n[English] [العربية] [Türkçe] \n# ![] Gold price today in Egypt\n24k22k21k18k14k10k6kGramTolaOunce100GramKiloUSDCADGBPEURRUBSARAEDINRIDRKRWCNYBRLTRYKWDIRRDZDAUDBHDEGPGHSIQDJODLBPLYDMXNMADOMRPKRQARSGDZARUZSYER\n$1.00 = EGP 46.93\n**EGP 231,515.80**\nFriday, January 30, 2026*Live*\nChange:-EGP 11,857.30(-4.87%)\nOpen:EGP 243,373.09\nHigh:EGP 243,373.09\nLow:EGP 226,814.54\n**