{"type":"message","id":"6f43d592","parentId":"1c4f2e56","timestamp":"2026-02-28T14:08:53.117Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-a407c09e8fe92cd2","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: Gold Price in Egypt Today – Live 24K, 22K, 21K Rates in EGP\nAuthor: \nPublished Date: 2025-03-04T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://goldpriceme.com/gold-price-in-egypt/\nText: Gold Price in Egypt Today –Live 24K, 22K, 21K Rates in EGP\n[Close Menu**] \n[**Facebook] [**X (Twitter)] [**Instagram] \n[**Facebook] [**X (Twitter)] [**Instagram] \n[] \nThursday, May 8, 2025\n[**] \nPrice Updated:Thursday, 8 May 2025\n[] \n[**] \n# Gold Price in Egypt\n## Today Gold Price in Egypt\nAs of Today,Thursday, May 8th, 2025, the Gold Price in Egypt is EGP 5,556.93 per Gram for 24 Carat Gold.\n|Gold Purity|Per Gram (EGP)|Per Tola (EGP)|\n24K Gold|EGP 5,556.93|EGP 64,757.64|\n22K Gold|EGP 5,101.26|EGP 59,447.51|\n21K Gold|EGP 4,862.32|EGP 56694.65|\n18K Gold|EGP 4,167.70|EGP 48,568.23|\n14K Gold|EGP 3,247.93|EGP 37,883.22|\n10K Gold|EGP 2,315.19|EGP 27,003.94|\nLast Update:Thursday, May 8th, 2025\nAds\n## 1 Tola Gold Price in Egypt\nToday,Thursday, May 8th, 2025, the Gold Rate in Egypt is EGP 64,757.64 per Tola for 24 Carat Gold.\n|Per Tola|Today Gold Price|\n24K Gold 1 Tola|EGP 64,757.64|\n22K Gold 1 Tola|EGP 59,447.51|\n21K Gold 1 Tola|EGP 56694.65|\n18K Gold 1 Tola|EGP 48,568.23|\n## 24K Gold Price in Egypt Today\n|Per Gram|Today Gold Price|\n1 Gram|EGP 5,556.93|\n5 Gram|EGP 2\n\nTitle: Egypt Gold Price Live - 24-hour (gold prices in Egyptian pounds EGP)\nURL: https://www.livepriceofgold.com/egypt-gold-price.html\nText: Egypt Gold Price Live - 24-hour (gold prices in Egyptian pounds EGP)\n[![live gold price]]![live] \n* ![Live SPOT Gold] SPOT GOLD\n3319.24$\n**-0.02**% (-0.66)\nHigh:**3319.89**| Low:**3319.24**\n* ![Gold Price per Gram] PER GRAM\n106.7280$\n**-0.02**\nHigh:**106.75**| Low:**106.75**\n* ![Gold Tola Price] PER TOLA\n1 244.854$\n**-0.25**\