ice per Gram | Price per Gram |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| [Gold 24k Carat] | 7,868.27 | 164.09 |\n| [Gold 22k Carat] | 7,212.58\n\nTitle: Gold Price Today in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP), Egypt Gold Rate\nAuthor: www.moneycurrencyconverter.com\nPublished Date: 2025-05-15T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://www.moneycurrencyconverter.com/gold-prices-today-in-egypt.html\nText: Gold Price Today in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP), Egypt Gold Rate\n\n# Current Gold Price Today in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP)\n\n1 Gold Ounce = 249,961.54 EGP 1 Gram Gold = 8,036.45 Egyptian Pound\n\nGold price in Egypt is calculated both per ounce, gram, kilogram and tola and for the most common karats. The following table displays current gold rates in Egypt in Egyptian Pound (EGP) for troy ounce, kilogram, tael, tola, pennyweight, grain and gram of different karats. Troy ounce is a traditional unit of gold weight. Gold prices per troy ounce are converted from USD to Egyptian Pound according to the latest exchange rates where 1 USD = 47.49 Egyptian Pound .\n\n## Price of Gold in Egyptian Pound\n\n| Gold Unit | Gold Price (EGP) |\n| --- | --- |\n| 1 Gram Gold | 8,036.45 EGP |\n| 1 Troy Ounce Gold | 249,961.54 EGP |\n| 1 Kilogram Gold | 8,036,450.11 EGP |\n| 1 Tael Gold | 300,796.22 EGP |\n| 1 Tola Gold | 93,735.58 EGP |\n| 1 Pennyweight Gold | 12,498.08 EGP |\n| 1 Grain Gold | 520.75 EGP |\n\nThe most commonly u\n\nTitle: Gold price today in Egypt\nURL: https://pricegold.net/eg-egypt/\nText: Gold price today in Egypt\n[![Gold price today] Gold priceToday] \n4:21:56 PMNY Time\nSunday, April 27, 2025\nEnglish\n[English] [العربية] [Türkçe] \n# ![] Gold price today in Egypt\n24k22k21k18k14k10k6kGramTolaOunce100GramKiloUSDCADGBPEURRUBSARAEDINRIDRKRWCNYBRLTRYKWDIRRDZDAUDBHDEGPGHSIQDJODLBPLYDMXNMADOMRPKRQARSGDZARUZSYER\n$1.00 = EGP 50.89\n**EGP 168,880.01**\nSunday, April 27, 2025*Live*\nChange:EGP 0.00(0%)\nOpen:EGP 168,880.01\nHigh:EGP 168,880.01\nLow:EGP 168,880.01\n**In Egypt**, the current price of go